    "high_level_description": "final one- or two-sentence Ideogram description",
    "style_description": {
      "aesthetics": "final aesthetics",
      "lighting": "final lighting",
      "photo": "camera/lens details for photographs, or omit this key for non-photo prompts",
      "medium": "photograph",
      "color_palette": ["#RRGGBB"]
    },
    "compositional_deconstruction": {
      "background": "final background / scene shell",
      "elements": []
    }
  }
}
The prompt_json value must be the final Ideogram caption object, not a string. If the caption is non-photographic, use art_style instead of photo and keep the official non-photo key order.

